msgid "?marketo=download"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "hero_url_text"
msgid "Download full framework"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "content_image_label"
msgid "FRAMEWORK"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "content_image_title"
msgid "What you'll discover:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "content_image_description"
msgid ""
"Using a total adult population in Hong Kong with investable assets (<b>85%</b> of the total online representative adult population in Hong Kong), YouGov segmented them based on the value of the "
"investable assets they have and the extent to which they look for profitable ways to invest money."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "content_image_description"
msgid "The segments have then been profiled to reveal the attitudes and behavioural traits of each group."
msgstr ""

